{
  "texts": [
    "Hovering over the clusters triggers a highlight effect and shows the cluster label.",
    "Users can select a cluster by clicking on the cluster label.",
    "This triggers the Document View to show articles in the cluster and the mentioned keywords (T3).",
    "Additionally, clicking on the cluster temporarily expands the cluster to expose its sub-structure (T1), as shown in Figure 6-b.",
    "The sub-structure is colored in different colors while maintaining the original cluster's shape."
  ]
}